Author: Bobsrepair
Title: [ANN] Bob's Repair [Token Sale Complete]
Body: We appreciate the questions and discussion. We announced our new road map towards the end of Q1 and published it as promised. Why did we wait so long to publish the new roadmap? Well we were still trying to figure out which direction should we go. We were in 13 cities sending jobs to many contractors and were burning through large amounts of capital (we even had a office in India with 8 dispatchers, including salaries for developers, team members etc) with that kind of burning we knew long term we wouldn’t make it so we asked ourselves what can we do to become profitable? How many crypto projects were profitable? All they do is sell their token reserves until they can’t sell anymore. A top 30 cryptocurrency six months ago fired 85% of their staff and closed down all their offices. When we heard this we knew it was time to solve one issue become profitable.   This is whe our CEO decided to scale down to one city and grow slowly. We went from sending out hundreds of leads a day to hiring full time staff members to do the jobs as Bob’s Repair. From January 28th to now we went from burning 50-150k a month to bringing in over 60k in revenue and becoming profitable. By hiring in house workers were were able to control pricing make it 50% less and also have a better understanding of material costs and day to day operation. Today alone we brought in over $3,500 in revenue. Our central costs are the same so it’s nice to see a larger profit margin.  We will publish our decentralized platform as announced in the roadmap but right now our major focus is increasing revenues (increasing the buyback program) hiring more full time employees to do jobs and expanding to Phoenix, Arizona.  We can proudly say we are making more money than spending and are here for the long run. Crypto winter is over for us. Winter isn’t coming.

Author: Bobsrepair
Title: [ANN] Bob's Repair [Token Sale Complete]
Body: We have a major announcement coming. We signed the agreement and are waiting for the go ahead. Also, couple exchanges will be listing us soon so please stay tuned for this as well. We are making sure every thing we do isn’t rushed. We are here for the long term and are generating real revenues. We will be adding couple hundred contractors and our new office is going to open in Chennai, India on October 25th. We will be training 5 new staff members and our manager before having them help us with couple hundred new contractors. With this said we do not want to grow too fast and want to make sure every move is calculated.  The markets are low which is a great opportunity for bob’s repair to differentiate from other projects. We have overcame many negative statistics.  The purpose of our new office in Chennai, India to help Bob’s Repair with customer service via text, email and phone calls. We personally believe the future is via text message in the form or regular texts and iMessage. Look how Apples new chat feature is done via iMessage. We will have an application IOS and Android for contractors and consumers but we believe consumers might only use our app 1-3 times a year for home repair.  We are way ahead of our December Q4 goals and are excited about the near future.

Author: Bobsrepair
Title: [ANN] Bob's Repair [Token Sale Complete]
Body: Bob's Repair buyback Rewards Program at 14 Cents.  Bob’s Repair sends home repair job calls to contractors throughout the USA. These contractors currently pay Bob’s Repair for every successful job call that is sent to them. The BOB Buyback Program was started in order to reward workers for their efforts by awarding them BOB Tokens after every job that they complete.  In the past, Bob’s Repair would keep the entire fee that contractors paid the company from each completed job. Now, the company takes ⅓ of the fee and uses it to buy BOB Tokens that are automatically awarded to contractors after the completion of a job.  The BOB Buyback program was created in order to allow Bob’s Repair to buy these tokens from the community every day in order to send them to contractors as a reward. Instead of buying the tokens from an exchange, the company has published this BOB Buyback smart contract that will automatically buy tokens directly from any interested sellers in the community, starting at $0.14 USD per token. Click here to sell your tokens. https://bobsrepair.com/buyback/  Bob’s Repair currently values BOB Tokens at the starting price of $0.14 USD.  The amount of BOB tokens purchased from the community will vary from day to day, depending on the amount of successful job calls that Bob’s Repair contractors complete that day. The company is currently making plans to expand its operations to 100 cities in the United States. As more contractors partner with Bob’s Repair and more job calls are sent to them, the company will need more BOB tokens to send to its contractors causing the company to purchase more BOB Tokens from the community for this reward system.  Sample Job Call:  For example, the last completed water heater installation generated $450 in profit for the contractor, with Bob’s Repair earning 15% of this fee, which is $67.50. One third of this 15% transaction fee, $22.5, is used to buy back BOB Tokens from the community at 14 cents per token which are then awarded to the contractor.    Please read our medium post.   https://medium.com/@BobsRepair/bobs-repair-buy-back-rewards-program-27ceb87da0a7

Author: Bobsrepair
Title: [ANN] Bob's Repair [Token Sale Complete]
Body: Announcing the BOB Token Community Lending Pool June 26, 2018   Summary: This proposal has been created to establish a means for FIAT customers to be able use the BOB Escrow and Blockchain system via www.BobsRepair.com without experiencing market fluctuations of the BOB Token Price by establishing a BOB Token Community Lending Pool and allowing FIAT customers to borrow the equivalent value of BOB tokens from other members of the BOB Network through this open-source community-driven lending pool.   The problem: In order to use the BOB Network Escrow and Blockchain Service for trusted home repairs and immutable reviews a customer is required to own and allocate BOB Tokens to every segment of this home repair/new construction job. However, since BOB Tokens are owned by the network, a collective group of entities worldwide, and are freely transferrable, the price of these tokens has the potential to vary. A customer and a contractor may not want to convert their FIAT into BOB Tokens through the course of time it takes to complete a job due to the potential for these market fluctuations and their effect on the amount of FIAT that the contractor would receive after finishing the job.   Solution: In order to provide FIAT customers BOB Tokens and decrease price volatility risk while still keeping the FIAT customer experience simple, the BOB Token Community Lending Pool is proposed.   The BOB Token Community Lending Pool is an open-source smart contract that will allow the BOB Community to send their BOB Tokens to it in order to lend their tokens to FIAT customers at the time of their payment. For example, if a customer is quoted $400 for an installation by a BOB Network Contractor, he/she can pay $400 using their credit card.   At the same time the customer agrees to borrow BOB Tokens from the BOB Token Community Lending Pool at a small cost, for example, $20 USD (the exact percentages and fee allocation are in the process of being finalized).   These funds, $400, are held by Bob’s Repair Inc., or a Bob’s Repair authorized payment processor or an escrow company, (depending on the jurisdiction) while the job is being completed, minus the example $20 Community Lending Fee. The $20 Community Lending fee is used to make an automatic BOB Token purchase off the market by the customer and is distributed to the BOB Token Community Lending Pool evenly.   Effect: As more FIAT transactions occur on the BOB Network more customers will require BOB Network Community members to lend them BOB Tokens to execute their home repair/new construction transactions.   The more FIAT transactions there are on the BOB Network the more BOB tokens will be required by these FIAT customers and the higher the return for community members staking their tokens will be. As FIAT transaction volumes grow more people will be incentivized to purchase tokens off of the market and stake them in the lending pool to take advantage of the interest earned from lending these tokens to FIAT customers.  Important disclaimer: Tokenomics related proposals made by Bob’s Repair, including the announcement regarding the BOB Token Community Lending Pool, are subject to evolve and change at any time in any capacity. Development of various Bob’s Repair tokenomics models are still in progress.

Author: Bobsrepair
Title: [ANN] Bob's Repair [Token Sale Complete]
Body: We are waiting for a larger purchase. A person asked us to give him couple more days. We are using these couple days for our Crypto Millionaire Raffle!    The Bob's Repair Team would like to end the main sale with maximum excitement by giving everyone a chance to become a crypto millionaire. One drawing will be done every single day, starting today. Six people will win 250,000 tokens, one person will win 500,000 tokens and someone will become a Crypto Millionaire!  All pre-sale and main sale participants who purchased 0.08 ETH worth of BOB tokens are automatically entered in the first drawing; however, only raffle entry participants who buy BOB tokens starting today until May 8 have a chance to win the 1 million BOB token grand prize .  We will be doing 7 more raffle drawings, with the second one being tomorrow (May 2, 2018). The rules are very simple. If you purchase 0.08 Ether of BOB tokens you receive 1 Raffle ticket. For every two raffle entries, you get one raffle entry for free. For example, if you were to buy 0.16 ETH worth of BOB tokens, you would get 2 raffle entries plus one bonus raffle entry. Our second drawing will include all everyone that contributed 0.08 ETH or more in the span of 24 hours on May 2. For further details explaining raffle bonuses, please read our medium post.  Prizes and Dates: *  May 1: 250,000 BOB Tokens (purchased 0.08 ETH in the pre-sale or main sale) Winner: Krishna! *  May 2: 250,000 BOB Tokens (purchased 0.08 ETH in that 24 hours) *  May 3: 250,000 BOB Tokens (purchased 0.08 ETH in that 24 hours) *  May 4: 250,000 BOB Tokens (purchased 0.08 ETH in that 24 hours) *  May 5: 250,000 BOB Tokens (purchased 0.08 ETH in that 24 hours) *  May 6: 250,000 BOB Tokens (purchased 0.08 ETH in that 24 hours) *  May 7: 500,000 BOB Tokens (purchased 0.08 ETH in that 24 hours) *  May 8: 1,000,000 BOB Tokens (purchased 0.08 ETH on or after May 1st)

Author: b1marlin
Title: [ANN] Bob's Repair [Token Sale Complete]
Body: Bob'sRepair : Eliminating Review Fraud with Trusted Transactions between home owners and contractors.  The founders of Bob's Repair have been connecting contractors to consumers since 2013, servicing 55,000 consumers and generating over $1,000,000 in income for their contractors through marketing initiatives. The two brothers then decided to utilize Blockchain technology to solve the great problems affecting the current home repair market by founding Bob's Repair. Bob’s Repair is a company that was created in order to eliminate review fraud in the skilled trade service industry by launching a decentralized website where anyone can search by previous transactions for any worker and see how much their services will cost--information that is stored in an unalterable fashion for everyone to see. The founders will onboard the previous 55,000 clients and workers to the portal immediately after launch. We are changing the world by starting with the contractors--who will believe lie at the most essential part--the heart--of our society.  Mission: Bob's Repair's mission is to completely eliminate fraud and intermediaries in the industry, bringing all consumers direct and low prices, transparency and a peace of mind when searching for a contractor.  Trust With Blockchain:Bob’s Repair is building a Trusted Transaction Network where consumers can define milestones with contractors and release funds upon completion of each project stage.  Nation-Wide Expansion:Since 2014 Bob’s Repair has serviced over 50,000 customers by connecting consumers to contractors through the proprietary Skilled Trade Worker Platform (STWP). We’re now staged to expand to the top-100 US Markets.  Smart Contracts for Smart Contractors: Bob’s Repair will leverage smart contracts to hold payments in escrow and issue them as milestones are completed. Author: Bobsrepair
Title: [ANN] Bob's Repair [Token Sale Complete]
Body: As the CEO of Bob's Repair, I felt we were not ready to deliver the best possible product and presence to the community. When my brother and I attended the Satoshi Roundtable we got to speak to a lot of successful founder/devs and pick their brains about their ICOs. (Fluffy Ponny- Monero, Anthony Dip Iorio - Etherium, Michael Terpin, Jeffrey Tucker, Andrew Filipowski, etc) I personally felt we were not ready to do our main sale mid March.  This is what is going on for the next three weeks prior to the main sale:  1. Currently in Seoul Korea: Finished with d10e conference and met with multiple investors and did two additional presentations. 2. Yesterday a mainstream Korean newspaper interviewed me about bobs repair. The article should be out shortly. 3. Heading to Hong Kong to do an interview with Bloomberg Magazine and be on the Bloomberg Radio Asia Worldwide. 4. In our Las Vegas office, we are doing a financial audit with a third party firm and making sure all token allocation is correct. 5. BuzzFeed will be releasing an article on me. (Until it is published it is not 100%) 6. Reuters will be doing an article on Bob's Repair (Until it is published it is not 100%) 7. Forbes will be doing a piece on us. (Until it is published it is not 100%) 8. Bitfilm.com is working on our commercial should be ready in couple days. 9. March 14th 1 million dollar airdrop with a referral system. 10. March 15th Heading to Puerto Rico for Coin Agenda 11. Our MVPs: Application, Website and SMS API will be released prior to the main sale 12. Announcing a massive partnership that is going to make a huge difference (stay tuned) 13. Hosho.io and Newalchemy.io are doing a security audit on our smart contract. Our team member Pavel Rubin has created over 15 smart contracts for other ICOs so we doubt they will find anything but better be double safe than sorry! 14. We added couple new team members to our organization. 15. March 20th and March 21st. Token2049 Conference in Hong Kong. 16. I have personally turned down a 3mln dollar investment and a 2mln dollar investment because the terms would not be favorable towards all the other people that purchased our tokens. I personally believe we need a high amount of people to have our token so that there is utility to it. One person having 10 mln BOB tokens is terrible for the community.  I am working around the clock with the team to make sure we provide the best possible product before the start of the main sale on April 4th. My brother has phenomena (due to over working himself) and unfortunately, I also got sick. The team and I are working the clock. Yesterday in Seoul I was in Wework for 18 hours and today I have been here 8 hours and will be here for another 5.    Anyways does anyone have any ideas of how we can announce our airdrop? I was thinking on doing something crazy like the time I jumped out of an airplane. hmm I am open to all suggestions!

Author: Bobsrepair
Title: [ANN] Bob's Repair [Token Sale Complete]
Body: Our bounty telegram is https://t.me/bobbounty you can get answers in real time.  Quote from: juicejoyce on February 12, 2018, 03:21:54 PM Congratulations to this project since the pre-sale was very successful and more than 6000 ETH has been raised, it is not so easy for a ico project to achieve that goal, I just want to know when will be the formal ICO?  We will be announcing our main sale date very shortly. Just discussing it with our board members and advisors.    Quote from: Emdppablo on February 11, 2018, 08:11:59 PM Quote from: Notin2 on February 11, 2018, 02:42:12 PM Quote from: Chikitita2004 on February 10, 2018, 08:53:43 AM Quote from: mylifeisfullofalts on February 09, 2018, 06:30:27 PM Different repairs are generally happening everyday in different areas of our community, electrical repairs, mechanical repairs, construction repairs and so on, and honestly finding a good contractor to do the job is quite frustrating. I believe in the power of blockchain technology , on how it can a record data and how no other people would be able to alter this input data. A public record of the labor pricing and labor reviews on the blockchain can greatly help lots of people in finding the right contractor that was given a good review based on services provided to their previous clients.   And another advantage here is the review they put or make in every contractor’s profile is reliable because they are the reviews previous clients made. Reviews based on experience and not just made by anyone else.  Yeah Bob's Repair bring a different approach to blockchain by creating such innovative idea to give a more decentralized system of labour pricing and making all kinds of repair in a more convenience manner, a very smart way of finding the best service.  Bob's repair's project is indeed incredible, but my question is how bob's repair differ from decentralized forum. Do bob's repair will have a KYC for the labourer? if none they can just create or add different name. I feel troublesome on this side since it's decentralized.  We are still deciding all the details but leaning towards a KYC. Not set in stone.

Author: mylifeisfullofalts
Title: [ANN] Bob's Repair [Token Sale Complete]
Body: Different repairs are generally happening everyday in different areas of our community, electrical repairs, mechanical repairs, construction repairs and so on, and honestly finding a good contractor to do the job is quite frustrating. I believe in the power of blockchain technology , on how it can a record data and how no other people would be able to alter this input data. A public record of the labor pricing and labor reviews on the blockchain can greatly help lots of people in finding the right contractor that was given a good review based on services provided to their previous clients.

Author: H. Veron
Title: [ANN] Bob's Repair [Token Sale Complete]
Body: The Review Fraud -It's not uncommon these days to hear news about companies leaving bad reviews on competitor's pages or buying reviews to inflate their own overall ratings. To curb the trust issues that consumers have due to such practices, the Bob Platform will be using Blockchain technology to tie down reviews of both sides - consumer and contractor - with the actual financial transaction. So, the platform will only present real and unadulterated reviews. This will help foster transparency and trust in the platform

Author: Bobsrepair
Title: [ANN] Bob's Repair [Token Sale Complete]
Body: We will have a utility token in the future and customers will be able to use it for iservices but as of today customers will be using FIAT to pay for services. Crypto will happen but the everyday skilled trade worker is not ready for it. We will have a website, application and will also use SMS API. With SMS API you can stores your CC, leave a review (tied to the steem blockchain) say how much was the labor, how much was the material and how long the job took.  It is very important that our system is user-friendly and compatible to every person. We will be launching our prototypes prior to the beginning of the main sale.

I can say yes! Bob's repair will give a lifetime warranty to us.

Author: Bobsrepair
Title: [ANN] Bob's Repair [Token Sale Complete]
Body: Hello! John McAfee is our Partner and Senior Advisor. He has tweeted about us multiple times and also is listed on our website bobsrepair.com   Bob's Repair is going to have an Escrow Service that funds will be released based on milestones. I do not think people will use it for smaller jobs like toilet installs but it will be needed for an AC install, kitchen remodels etc. Since 2014 we dealt with a lot of issues where the consumer would screw the contractor and even the other way around where the job wasn't done properly. All our reviews will be tied to the transaction.   We are about to announce a 1000 ETH investment and our bonus phase will drop down to 20%. So hurry up and jump on that 23% before it is too late!

We will continue to update our investors and users as we build our platform and launch our decentralized applications.  Being able to find a contractor at a low price and preventing advertisers from taking money away from contractors is a service that should have been launched a long time ago, but has never been. Now, thanks to Blockchain technologies, we have the opportunity to do so and educate the community on why decentralized platforms, such as Bob’s Repair, are eliminating review fraud and unfair pricing in their respective industries.  Thank you for supporting our project.

Author: Bobsrepair
Title: [ANN] Bob's Repair [Token Sale Complete]
Body: Thank you for asking! We are an ERC20 Token. The Bob Application will leverage blockchain technology to fight review fraud. The Bob Application will be built on the STEEM blockchain due to its three second transaction time and no transaction costs. The Bob Application will store all financial transactions that take place on Bob’s Repair on the blockchain. Then, when both sides of a transaction - consumer and contractor - leave a review, Bob’s Repair will link that review to the actual financial transaction. By linking reviews with actual financial transactions, consumers can trust that the review is real and unaltered. Real reviews, from real consumers, provides better information so consumers can make better decisions.  Our Revenue Mode:  To keep prices low for customers and barriers of entry low for contractors, Bob’s Repair will not have membership fees, sign-up costs, or transaction fees. Instead, Bob’s Repair will generate revenue in three ways: the STEEM blockchain, escrow services, and providing targeted beneficial third-party services to contractors and consumers.  ● Escrow Services. For transactions where the parties desire to use an escrow service, Bob’s Repair will earn a 1.5 percent service fee from the funds held in escrow. For escrow services, Bob’s Repair will leverage blockchain technology to ensure that project milestones, reviews, and associated data are stored in tamper-proof format. ● Third-Party Services. To generate revenue and provide further benefits to contractors and consumers, Bob’s Repair will provide targeted loans, insurance products, and decentralized financial products and services for both contractors and consumers ● STEEM Blockchain. Use of the STEEM blockchain will result in revenue for Bob’s Repair.

Title: [ANN] Bob's Repair [Token Sale Complete]
Body: Quote from: AncientMystery on December 30, 2017, 02:23:57 PM I will invest if John McAfee will tweet about your ICO   He has tweeted about us multiple times. We will be doing an interview with him in couple of days. I will post a link.   Quote from: siddartha1492 on December 29, 2017, 04:38:31 PM Hmm, the big question is how will you get trusted reviews? People who can be influenced by an incentive to post fake reviews on normal sites can also do the same on a blockchain based website. So how does blockchain protect from fake reviews? Between, John McAfee's ICO reviews are no longer trusted!!!  The reviews will be tied to the transaction. There could be couple bad actors but they won't be able to act bad for long because every review will be stored and won't be able to be altered. Now let's just say some contractor finds 4 people and goes through the whole process..the 5th, 6th, and 7th real client will expose him for high pricing, crappy work etc..people will have their transaction tied to the review that will specifically talk about the pricing, time it, what was fixed etc. The issue with home advisor and other skilled trade marketplaces is that they delete bad reviews because these contractors threaten that they won't pay them any more for leads. The worse part is that three guys are charged $30-$75 bucks per lead and only one of them gets the job. This fee is pinned on the customer, therefore, making a simple toilet install super expensive.   GOODBYE PRICE GAUGING, GOODBYE NO TRANSPARENCY, GOODBY ADVERTISING FEES

Author: hastalavista
Title: [ANN] Bob's Repair [Token Sale Complete]
Body: Ok guys, I only can encourage everbody to NOT participate. Why?  So I saw their video in which they promise 21st 40 pages whitepaper. On 26th I ask them where the whitepaper is on Telegram. https://youtu.be/LzREamiDMBk?t=1m07s  bytheway the video was published on the 21st on youtube   They answer on telegram: "So sorry, we definitely meant whitepaper summary."  But that is 3 pages and not 40 pages. They explicitly say 40 pages whitepaper on 21st December in the video.  So next they tell me on Telegram: "We are working so hard to get things done and we will publish it in the night 25th to 26th. Definitely it will be published... Our legal team is holding us back and the holiday season is not helping"  Then I tell them I find this unprofessional how they handle it - then they kick me out of their Telegram channel. I was not rude, I was realistic and not an asshole...I just told them what they say makes no sense and it was unprofessional...  Wow  So they did not review the video and saw:  Hey we said whitepaper and not whitepaper summary...no, they put it online and afterwards when they cannot deliver in time they tell everyone they really meant whitepaper summary...but the real WP is coming very soon and  the whole team is working so hard. Then suddenly their lawyers are the reason the WP wasn't published yet. I haven't seen anything that justifies  6000 BOB tokens are worth 1 Ether.
